LEADING RETAIL POWER EXCHANGE TOPS $250 MILLION IN ENERGY 
TRANSACTIONS USING EXCELERGY TECHNOLOGY
 
 
 
World Energy Solutions announced that more than $250 million worth of natural gas and power - 2.5 billion kilowatt hours of electricity alone - was bought and sold on its Internet-based exchange during 2001. Who delivered the solution behind their growing success? Excelergy!
 
 
 
To learn more about how Excelergy's product leadership empowers World Energy Solutions to be a top performing retail energy market operator, just click here:
 
 
 
  <http://www.excelergy.com/images/purple_arrow.gif>  www.excelergy.com/news/jan29-02.html <http://www.excelergy.com/news/jan29-02.html>
 
 
 
